### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJlbWFpbCI6ImFkbWluQGd3YW5zaG9wLmNvbSIsInN1YiI6IjEiLCJyb2xlIjoiQURNSU4iLCJpYXQiOjE3Mjg1OTU2MDB9.example

### Listar todos os ingressos
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obter ingresso por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obter ingressos do usuário
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets/user/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obter ingressos do evento
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets/event/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar ingresso (comprar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "eventId": "1",
  "categoryId": "1",
  "quantity": 2
}

### Validar ingresso
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/validate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "qrCodeData": "TICKET_1_2024-06-15_20:00"
}

### Usar ingresso
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tickets/1/use
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Transferir ingresso
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tickets/1/transfer
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "newUserName": "Maria Santos",
  "newUserEmail": "maria@email.com"
}

### Cancelar ingresso
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tickets/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obter estatísticas de ingressos
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obter estatísticas de ingressos por evento
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets/stats?eventId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
